things went downhill after she was disqualified before the final after breaching the 50kg weight limit.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A day after her heartbreaking disqualification, Vinesh announced her decision to retire from wrestling.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also made a plea to the court of arbitration for sport (CAS) to award her a joint silver medal.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0200976588310587e-20, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The CAS deferred the verdict a couple of times and eventually dismissed the application filed by Vinesh for a silver medal in the women's 50kg event at Paris.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 934, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0200976588310587e-20, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999835372365, \"rank\": 1.6462749410722517e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite not receiving a medal for her efforts and landmark wins at the Olympics, an excited crowd of thousands welcomed the wrestler like they would have welcomed with a medal around her neck on August 17.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People thronged the roadsides to catch a glimpse of one of the country's most celebrated athletes of recent times, waiting to exchange a few words and get a selfie with her.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was welcomed with garlands and flowers in her hometown, Bhiwani.\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhiwani_district\", \"score\": 0.9752183348857565, \"rank\": 0.025411385068879126, \"text\": \"Bhiwani\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhiwani_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bhiwani_district\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since announcing her retirement, Vinesh has hinted towards a possible change in heart and reversing her decision.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement that she posted on her social media account, Vinesh said, \\\"Maybe under different circumstances, I could see myself playing till 2032 because the fight in me and wrestling in me will always be there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1716, \"end\": 1722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}]}"